collection.name: OnChainMonkey
collection.description:
OnChainMonkey is the innovative NFT project by Danny Yang, Amanda Terry, Bill Tai, and Metagood. The NFTs are the first on chain pfp collection created in a single transaction, and provide membership into the OnChainMonkey community. We were awarded Fast Company’s 20 Best World Changing Ideas for Impact Investing and one of 8 finalists in the Coindesk x Extreme Tech Challenge Web3 competition. Meet some of our community. https://onchainmonkey.com/team

For the OCM Dessert Collection, head here: https://opensea.io/collection/ocm-dessert
